{"tid":163113,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"考車時停車拉手掣問題","createTime":"2017-03-19T17:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T10:34:03.000Z","uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"502e259e3eea7daa433fcef37e8f1186d257c2d7","tid":163113,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T17:30:44.000Z","msg":"黎緊考棍van<br />\n但唔清楚係咪停車都要拉手掣<br />\n<br />\n例如條路中間突然要停低<br />\n係咪收油，踩極力子，拉埋手掣，再重新開車？<br />\n咁好似好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef454ae40c217f2b8d094428cb7f7f7663103ee1","tid":163113,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T18:23:09.000Z","msg":"如果你覺得好短時間會再起步咪唔使拉囉，其實拉咪仲方便，放晒腳唔使力。<br />\n上斜停的話諗都唔使諗拉左先啦，廢事溜後。"},{"pid":"d2f8afcb1b69c41b1dde98356ce2c33502712cb7","tid":163113,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T18:39:35.000Z","msg":"如果你平路停幾秒咪唔好拉<br />\n上斜就老閪都拉啦"},{"pid":"29883d2d61f95a5d2d28f9cf48d43a36f76c87f5","tid":163113,"uid":90304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T23:15:03.000Z","msg":"要拉，做樣比考官睇等佢知道你識拉手制"},{"pid":"1c62be2625d226d4a9a8c561abdd81401f01467f","tid":163113,"uid":2595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T23:22:46.000Z","msg":"行緊塞下車可以唔拉吊住極力子，等紅燈停得耐就點都拉"},{"pid":"bca367d2a3839571447b6d945b838c356ce889d1","tid":163113,"uid":68986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T23:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你覺得好短時間會再起步咪唔使拉囉，其實拉咪仲方便，放晒腳唔使力。<br />\n上斜停的話諗都唔使諗拉左先啦，廢事溜後。</blockquote><br />\n考車點都拉左先最隱陣 開車慢咪慢 最緊要合格 <br />\n之前試過係紅綠燈位吊極力子都比師傅屌"},{"pid":"4c463cd7b37f5aa3e1b9580827d31bf5f9afcffb","tid":163113,"uid":17516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T23:37:30.000Z","msg":"考車拉左一定冇死錯人"},{"pid":"dbbb9092bfc92f2562afe9404fbed8c6452778cb","tid":163113,"uid":44493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T23:52:34.000Z","msg":"考試就拉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n費事輸d姑寒位喇"},{"pid":"5d257691e730de6b389024ae7ccb9df4058db901","tid":163113,"uid":28054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T23:57:04.000Z","msg":"如果馬路寫住個停就100%停<br />\n其他你就可以睇情況 唔通轉綠燈 但前面車未開你又走去拉手制咩"},{"pid":"996b972981716bf3e48866100effdcb3ecd88e08","tid":163113,"uid":1724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:10:55.000Z","msg":"考試拉左實無死<br />\n到時考完理得你拉唔拉"},{"pid":"c803ee1f13267a83ada5236167a13bbd6e04cb8b","tid":163113,"uid":43721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:14:39.000Z","msg":"師傅教停燈一定要拉<br />\n讓路處、塞車唔洗拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b58cc08a816721aed41bf84c625554415513d3","tid":163113,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:27:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師傅教停燈一定要拉<br />\n讓路處、塞車唔洗拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有停牌就拉啦"},{"pid":"1105c65e52c1191920717c2a281206494847c95f","tid":163113,"uid":13908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:32:47.000Z","msg":"停死一定拉，考試做足全套啦大佬"},{"pid":"e9d6e7d5e040151ebcf984a130bb55dc6162405d","tid":163113,"uid":1424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T01:34:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果你覺得好短時間會再起步咪唔使拉囉，其實拉咪仲方便，放晒腳唔使力。<br />\n上斜停的話諗都唔使諗拉左先啦，廢事溜後。</blockquote><br />\n考車點都拉左先最隱陣 開車慢咪慢 最緊要合格 <br />\n之前試過係紅綠燈位吊極力子都比師傅屌</blockquote><br />\n呢個真，合格最緊要"},{"pid":"36947cc1b4537a2b49b3365d5a46167e0a6e750d","tid":163113,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TO04fue.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTO04fue.jpg&h=83b8e628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n師傅就話呢啲讓路口 唔洗拉手掣空波都得<br />\n可以落break停定 再落1波 Hold住個break 吊定極力子一有位就望左右鏡出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/20/150535_1061ca65189013f1d390a2d0c22e1c82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F20%2F150535_1061ca65189013f1d390a2d0c22e1c82.jpg&h=cd10a37a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢啲路口就唔洗諗啦 停車拉手掣空波<br />\n<br />\n當然兩個情況都可以停車拉手掣空波 呢樣真係做多好過做少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4730772c8dd8a424592f746b26c8353554b6cf","tid":163113,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T07:30:44.000Z","msg":"讓路位唔好拉<br />\n準備隨時出路口<br />\n拉左手制再重新起步好易miss左機會<br />\n冇車就收一收慢再出<br />\n唔停多過十秒都唔好拉"},{"pid":"cf03a9c9d55813e7075f3bc49fee2913fa88c3bc","tid":163113,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T00:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>讓路位唔好拉<br />\n準備隨時出路口<br />\n拉左手制再重新起步好易miss左機會<br />\n冇車就收一收慢再出<br />\n唔停多過十秒都唔好拉</blockquote><br />\n考試讓路位唔好拉？"},{"pid":"60154395feaa2b9fbe337b5207c2cfb19e63ce7c","tid":163113,"uid":8231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T00:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>讓路位唔好拉<br />\n準備隨時出路口<br />\n拉左手制再重新起步好易miss左機會<br />\n冇車就收一收慢再出<br />\n唔停多過十秒都唔好拉</blockquote><br />\n考試讓路位唔好拉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讓路位前先1波吊極力子慢慢印出去望右左右<br />\n<br />\n如前面有好多車過緊，例如3架或以上，要拉，等尾2架車過緊時，踩定極力子入1波鬆手制預備開車<br />\n<br />\n如無車就比油快手轉出去"},{"pid":"48ef61de2295851313f0d5cb3fc99c918b5a16e1","tid":163113,"uid":73677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讓路位唔好拉<br />\n準備隨時出路口<br />\n拉左手制再重新起步好易miss左機會<br />\n冇車就收一收慢再出<br />\n唔停多過十秒都唔好拉</blockquote><br />\n考試讓路位唔好拉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讓路位前先1波吊極力子慢慢印出去望右左右<br />\n<br />\n如前面有好多車過緊，例如3架或以上，要拉，等尾2架車過緊時，踩定極力子入1波鬆手制預備開車<br />\n<br />\n如無車就比油快手轉出去</blockquote><br />\n我過紅綠橙未轉燈果時已經1波吊極力子<br />\n(當然自己知道差唔多轉燈)<br />\n之後一轉燈鬆手街就即行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d17a1894da0825d2c4e0e8e2bafc4b725ca640","tid":163113,"uid":73677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:36:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讓路位唔好拉<br />\n準備隨時出路口<br />\n拉左手制再重新起步好易miss左機會<br />\n冇車就收一收慢再出<br />\n唔停多過十秒都唔好拉</blockquote><br />\n考試讓路位唔好拉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讓路位前先1波吊極力子慢慢印出去望右左右<br />\n<br />\n如前面有好多車過緊，例如3架或以上，要拉，等尾2架車過緊時，踩定極力子入1波鬆手制預備開車<br />\n<br />\n如無車就比油快手轉出去</blockquote><br />\n我過紅綠橙未轉燈果時已經1波吊極力子<br />\n(當然自己知道差唔多轉燈)<br />\n之後一轉燈鬆手制就即行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3b3a785585d52a5c32f01c5947bac94d53b005a3","tid":163113,"uid":7754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T02:07:34.000Z","msg":"嗰時師傅教，架車要停定既就要拉。<br />\n例如停紅燈，停字牌<br />\n<br />\n如果讓字但你睇清楚無車可以直出，就只需收慢，唔洗手掣"},{"pid":"4c12025271c120b836f8e13bcaa21b612ebbda26","tid":163113,"uid":70689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T13:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>讓路位唔好拉<br />\n準備隨時出路口<br />\n拉左手制再重新起步好易miss左機會<br />\n冇車就收一收慢再出<br />\n唔停多過十秒都唔好拉</blockquote><br />\n考試讓路位唔好拉？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n讓路位前先1波吊極力子慢慢印出去望右左右<br />\n<br />\n如前面有好多車過緊，例如3架或以上，要拉，等尾2架車過緊時，踩定極力子入1波鬆手制預備開車<br />\n<br />\n如無車就比油快手轉出去</blockquote><br />\n我過紅綠橙未轉燈果時已經1波吊極力子<br />\n(當然自己知道差唔多轉燈)<br />\n之後一轉燈鬆手制就即行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁樣揸<br />\n但同讓線拉唔拉手制冇乜關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54cd4af1979757a9c122a4c5887d7ceae8f1eb04","tid":163113,"uid":8582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T01:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TO04fue.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTO04fue.jpg&h=83b8e628&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n師傅就話呢啲讓路口 唔洗拉手掣空波都得<br />\n可以落break停定 再落1波 Hold住個break 吊定極力子一有位就望左右鏡出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/20/150535_1061ca65189013f1d390a2d0c22e1c82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F20%2F150535_1061ca65189013f1d390a2d0c22e1c82.jpg&h=cd10a37a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢啲路口就唔洗諗啦 停車拉手掣空波<br />\n<br />\n當然兩個情況都可以停車拉手掣空波 呢樣真係做多好過做少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我考試嗰陣就係讓路口諗住好快行得<br />\n二波停冇拉手制<br />\n結果想行就死咗火<br />\n（學車加考試死第二次火）<br />\n<br />\n得一半魂魄揸架車番去<br />\n好彩冇肥，不過嚇鳩死"},{"pid":"1f586594121e86d431cc5e9517fa5a17c99598b0","tid":163113,"uid":390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我考試嗰陣就係讓路口諗住好快行得<br />\n二波停冇拉手制<br />\n結果想行就死咗火<br />\n（學車加考試死第二次火）<br />\n<br />\n得一半魂魄揸架車番去<br />\n好彩冇肥，不過嚇鳩死</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2波停要落返1波喎<br />\n踩住break吊定極力子<br />\n有位就鬆break扭出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92f7a374ff4a017fff22e1fbfc1a08b0776bd4d","tid":163113,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T10:20:56.000Z","msg":"拉咗實冇死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}